{"tid":2259811,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登：特朗普咁玩分分鐘會贏","createTime":"2020-10-27T06:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T07:32:32.000Z","uid":278587,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e98822f0724db57df27cd1befd6052691ec8227d","tid":2259811,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:12:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2786024/10261_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2786024%2F10261_1024.jpg&h=8b13593a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國大選尚餘不足10天，全國有近6000萬選民已提早投票。早前美國哥倫比亞廣播公司的《60分鐘時事雜誌》訪問兩位總統候選人，總統特朗普（Donald Trump）中途憤然離場，民主黨候選人拜登（Joe Biden）卻透露，特朗普有機會勝出大選要憑什麼招數。<br />\n<br />\n據美國有線新聞網（CNN）等主流媒體的民調顯示，目前拜登領先特朗普。拜登在訪問中坦言，從未低估對手特朗普，又明言特朗普想要在大選中勝出，其招數之一就是不承認總統大選結果（delegitimizing the race's outcome is &quot;how he plays）。<br />\n<br />\n當兩位候選人得票接近，其中一方不承認結果，會交由最高法院審理，如2000年布殊總統（George W. Bush）和其時民主黨候選人戈爾（Al Gore）一樣。<br />\n<br />\n今年受疫情影響，多個州分允許選民以郵寄選票的方式投票。總統特朗普多次反對這個方式，指出郵寄選票容易出現選舉舞弊。若這次大選雙方不承認點票結果，將會交由最高法院審理。<br />\n<br />\n目前全國有近6000萬選民已提早投票，拜登在訪問中說：<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>「我認為我跟特朗普之間明顯的分別在於我們的世界觀和價值觀。」<br />\n<br />\n（But I think the contrast between Donald Trump and me is about as stark as it can get in terms of our value set and how we view the world.）</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n又自信道：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em>「總統先生，你的對手是拜登。拜登是一個長期以來往績優秀的人。」<br />\n<br />\n（Mr. President, you're running against Joe Biden. Joe Biden has a deep, steep, and successful record over a long, long time.）</em></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2786024/【美國大選】拜登受訪坦言%20「特朗普咁玩分分鐘會贏」?mtc=20042\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2786024%2F%E3%80%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%B8%E3%80%91%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E5%8F%97%E8%A8%AA%E5%9D%A6%E8%A8%80%2520%E3%80%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E5%92%81%E7%8E%A9%E5%88%86%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E6%9C%83%E8%B4%8F%E3%80%8D%3Fmtc%3D20042&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETXs01o1BQ7dYS%2FTJpuaPCiE%3D&h=ef5076cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2786024/【美國大選】拜登受訪坦言%20「特朗普咁玩分分鐘會贏」?mtc=20042</a>"},{"pid":"cbc381a219cc2992dc3aeab34a00c4183ff19083","tid":2259811,"uid":188176,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"總統先生，你的對手是拜登。拜登是一個長期以來往績優秀的人<br />\n<br />\n選輸3次總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3d5647a1f68e807e7e91b628963ca0470ecdce2","tid":2259811,"uid":40763,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:15:41.000Z","msg":"講咁撚多做咩<br />\n一句 連登仝人恭祝拜登當選<br />\n完"},{"pid":"0a53440a030d8dfb0065da943e1d051139e0f04d","tid":2259811,"uid":2054,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cbc381a219cc2992dc3aeab34a00c4183ff19083","tid":2259811,"uid":188176,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"總統先生，你的對手是拜登。拜登是一個長期以來往績優秀的人<br />\n<br />\n選輸3次總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:18:03.000Z","msg":"I am going to beat Joe Biden<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35d3d5ccf9cfece8b3cd37847a42d1ca83955a1","tid":2259811,"uid":183758,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:19:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">This is Democrats!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fprsdf6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFprsdf6.jpg&h=4d57595c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb9dd79c547c23f650a642c7cd8893b9fbc83134","tid":2259811,"uid":16057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"cbc381a219cc2992dc3aeab34a00c4183ff19083","tid":2259811,"uid":188176,"like":1