 />\n避免拜登當選之後爆發醜聞<br />\n<br />\n落選點都好過做做下辭職咁羞家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54da8a539f93dace2c5ea4ca033689fa6cc883bf","tid":2259811,"uid":30067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08997c0c896e6f779b6e5901b52f5c8344506a95","tid":2259811,"uid":196924,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cbc381a219cc2992dc3aeab34a00c4183ff19083","tid":2259811,"uid":188176,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:15:25.000Z","msg":"總統先生，你的對手是拜登。拜登是一個長期以來往績優秀的人<br />\n<br />\n選輸3次總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T06:24:50.000Z","msg":"西拜登東楚瑜。未聽過?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:32:05.000Z","msg":"東個個真正選一次姐<br />\n另外兩次界下票冇當過佢係選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6907d4cbdcc1b3b5bdd02bd4d6a601c5146302","tid":2259811,"uid":1425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-27T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"拜生識講中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}